{"logo":"https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=8&quality=60&sec=1534504253&di=d8f2196fc938254e4806830f2e8e4d1e&src=http%3A%2F%2Fg.hiphotos.baidu.com%2Fxiaodu%2Fpic%2Fitem%2F91ef76c6a7efce1b7b0b62e6a751f3deb48f65fe.jpg","summary":"四川民族学院是一所省属全日制普通本科院校，位于情歌的故乡——四川省康定市。学校入选四川省卓越法律人才教育培养计划、四川省卓越农林人才教育培养计划，是康巴藏区和四川省民族地区唯一一所民族本科高校，是省级“园林式校园”。学校肇始于1985年设立“康定民族师范专科学校”。1992年，学校更名为“康定民族师范高等专科学校”。2009年，经教育部批准，升格改建为四川民族学院。截至2017年9月，学校设有14个二级学院，举办有27个本科专业、12个专科专业和少数民族本专科预科，涵盖文、理、教、管、法、农、工、史、艺9个学科门类，有全日制在校生近9000人。校园占地面积600余亩，校舍建筑面积近25万平方米。教学科研仪器设备总值8223万元，图书馆藏纸质图书95万册。","tags":["民族类","本科","公办"],"attrs":{"创建时间":"1985","所在地区":"四川省康定县姑咱镇文化路4号","院校隶属":"四川省人民政府"},"imgs":["https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534504253&di=3d2f75f195ff287e30d93c9e2c110dac&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3639232979%2C692967755%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534504253&di=b628c9410a74aba5be86bfd74e7b6846&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3758450935%2C883540482%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534504253&di=61611f841357fef07a2074e656567d77&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3673134816%2C780744714%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534504253&di=e76136967da68b544cb319c4a73ead72&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D2730694259%2C2746350198%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534504253&di=e6754eb78b6f52061b87a031f9fac93e&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3507107094%2C4048481401%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm